dmca.title: TravelChinaGuide Discovers Copied Pages
dmca.body:
Dear Google, Inc.

1. I, the webmaster of www.travelchinaguide.com, am on behalf of our
company, Xi'an Diamond Network Co. Ltd. I am looking forward for your
concerns about the websites copied the below pages from our website.

The offender is www.beijingimpression.com. They copied 26 pages of contents
from our website. So we are here to ask for your investigation and removal
of the infringing pages.

One more thing I would like to mention here is that our website
www.travelchinaguide.com regularly updates our content to ensure the
accuracy of the info. Thus we found that some of the contents they copied
are now our old versions. We
